data.description:
Union County living on 2.38 acres, yet close to restaurants, shopping, 485 & 74.  Come and see this totally renovated ranch!

The home has been completed gutted to the studs. TOO many features to list! Just mentioning a few:

All new electrical, HVAC, plumbing fixtures, piping and tankless WH, New Kitchen Aid Appliances, white soft close cabinets in kitchen, pot filler over stove,  granite counter topsw/tile backsplash, farm sink, new deck, new covered stone front porch, real 3/4 inch hardwood floors throughout, 12.5 ceilings with custom crown moulding, upgraded fixtures and tile in baths. All work to home was permitted and passed inspection.   Fenced in backyard.  Union County schools!
